text: Jennifer O'Connor (born 13 April 1984 in Bundaberg, Australia) is an Australian netball player. She played with the Queensland Firebirds from 2006–07 in the Commonwealth Bank Trophy, and from 2008–09 in the ANZ Championship. ==References== *2008/09 Queensland Firebirds profile.
